name: Talia_v%27laenya
content:
Talia v'laenya was a female Bothan spy who lived during the time of the Galactic Civil War. Early during the conflict, she joined the Alliance to Restore the Republic and was a member of the Alliance Spy Network. However, she left the organization due to "unresolved differences" prior to the Battle of Yavin. In 1 ABY, she operated out of Nym's Stronghold on Lok. There, she encountered a spacer and provided information about Kimogila Town and the Canyon Corsair's Stronghold.
Talia v'laenya was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Talia v'laenya was added to the game with the "Publish 5" update, released on December 16, 2003.
